headline: Monolithic Power Systems (MPWR) Stock Trades Up, Here Is Why
summary: Shares of power management chips maker Monolithic Power Systems (NASDAQ:MPWR) jumped 9.5% in the afternoon session after investors grew more optimistic that an escalating trade war with China could be avoided.
